        <h3><span>Explore Your Inner Van Gogh</span></h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Overnight accommodations</li>
          <li>2 VIP tickets to the Art Institute of Chicago and <em>Van Gogh’s Bedrooms</em>, allowing all-inclusive museum access and bypassing the ticket line</li>
